	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>On your command, necromantic energies wash through your target, draining away vitality.</em></p><p><strong>[[/save constitution]]{Constitution Save}</strong></p><p>If you target a &amp;reference[plant]{plant} creature or a magical plant, it makes the saving throw with disadvantage, and you don't roll damage, instead dealing maximum damage. This spell has no effect on creatures that don't have water in their bodies.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> Target takes [[/damage 8d8 necrotic]] damage.*</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> Half damage.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*</strong> <strong>Upcasting:</strong> Increase damage by [[/damage 1d8 necrotic]]{1d8} for each spell level above 4th.</p>",
